Package ucd_2001_fe Description

The ucd_2001_fe package stores classes which constitutes a front end to the UCD_2001 Roadway Dispersion Model. This package provides a simple graphical front end to allow users to determine the concentration of pollutants near roadways based on meteorological information, roadway geometry and usage, and receptor location.

Version:
1.0 (December 2001)
Author:
Tony Held
